snippet.title: Johnny Depp Claims “No One Is Safe” In Cancel Culture  | THR News
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp took aim at cancel culture and described it as being “so far out of hand” while discussing his fall from grace in Hollywood during an appearance at the San Sebastian Film Festival.

 To learn more about this story:
